<!-- header -->

<div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid bg-dark mb-0">
  <div class="container">
    <img src="/assets/img/KLIbutton.gif" width=150 height=150 class="float-left" alt="Klingon Language Institute">
    <h1 class="display-4">tlhIngan ghoj!</h1>
    <h2 class="display-6">Learn Klingon!</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- dividing bar and help -->

<div class="container-fluid m-0 pt-0 pb-3 bg-dark text-center">
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModalCenter">
    What does this do?
  </button>

  <!-- Modal -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModalCenter" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalCenterTitle"
    aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-dialog-scrollable" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content bg-dark">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalCenterTitle">Welcome to Learn Klingon</h5>
          <!--          <button type="button btn-warning" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button> -->
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <P><i>nuqneH, taghwIâ€™ qaStaH nuq?</i></P>

          <P>That means "welcome, beginner! what's happening?" in Klingon.
          </P>
          <P>Learn Klingon is an initiative from the <a href="https://www.kli.org/">Klingon Language Institue</a> to
            help
            non-Klingons master the Klingon Language.
          </P>
          <P>The program is very simple.
          </P>
          <P>On the left, you have a series of Klingon words, under the heading "Klingon words being learned".
          </P>
          <P>Each word has a button. If you think you have mastered the Klingon word, click on the button to move it to
            the right side, under the heading "Klingon words mastered"
          </P>
          <P>If you changed your mind, you can move it back with the matching button.
          </P>
          <P>If you are not sure what the button does, the icon should give you a clue, or you can hover the pointing
            device over the button to receive a hint.
          </P>
          <P>You may only delete a Klingon word after you have mastered it.
          </P>
          <P>Should these Klingon words proven to be insufficient challange, or you have previously mastered some other
            Klingon words, please add them to this program in order to track your progress of Klingon language mastery.
          </P>

          <P>You are welcome to add more Klingon words you wish to master to this program, either using KLI resources,
            or using <a href="https://www.bing.com/translator">Microsoft Bing Translator</a>. Be warned that machine
            translation
            quality is low, and while you may get your meaning across, you will likely be laughed at, thus the need for
            this program, so you may master the Klingon language the proper way.
          </P>

        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer text-center">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- the actual left right interface -->

<div class="container-fluid m-0 p-3 bg-dark">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-1"></div>
    <div class="col-5">
      <h2>tlhIngan mu'mey ghoj!</h2>
      <h4>Klingon words being learned!</h4>

      {{#each klingons}}
      {{#unless mastered}}
      {{> klingons/klingon-block mastered=true}}
      {{/unless}}
      {{/each}}

    </div>
    <div class="col-5">
      <h2>tlhIngan mu'mey bobaghlu'!</h2>
      <h4>Klingon words mastered!</h4>

      {{#each klingons}}
      {{#if mastered}}
      {{> klingons/klingon-block mastered=false}}
      {{/if}}
      {{/each}}

    </div>
    <div class="col-1"></div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid m-0 p-3 bg-dark">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-1"></div>
    <div class="col-10">


      <h2>tlhIngan mu'mey chel</h2>
      <h4>Add a Klingon Word</h4>
      <form class="create-form">

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="ca">Klingon Word:</label>
          <input type="text" id="kw" name="kword">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="ca">English Translation:</label>
          <input type="text" id="en" name="english">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="sleepy">Mastered?</label><br>
          <P><input type="radio" name="mastered" value="1"> Hija'(yes)</P>
          <P><input type="radio" name="mastered" value="0" checked> ghobe' (no)</P>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class=" btn-warning btn-lg" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom"
          title="Add it!">maj <i class="fas fa-check"></i></button>
      </form>

    </div>
    <div class="col-1"></div>
  </div>
</div>